825585-6111<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">公司主页：http://www.chinasofti.com</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h6</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;color: royalblue&quot;</span>&gt;</span>招聘邮箱：<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">zhaopin2@chinasoftti.com</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="运行展示-1"><a href="#运行展示-1" class="headerlink" title="运行展示"></a>运行展示</h3><p><img src="C:\Myblog\source\img\image-20250827122641566.png" alt="image-20250827122641566"></p><h1 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h1><p>html是一种<strong>超文本标记语言</strong>，主要由<strong>标签</strong>构成。</p>]]></content>
      
      
